quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,"Nditsuba khufise!"
  103,2,"Toto bwene omundu ali mu khusikha (abula inganga)."
  103,3,"Halali balia basuubila, mana nibakhola amalayi, ne nibachelanila okhwema khubwatoto, ne nibachelanila okhwifwiila."
  104,1,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo shilinyoola buli umoonyanga khubikhole nende khumakhuwa!"
  104,2,"Ulia wabunjelesia omwandu mana nakubala."
  104,3,"Aparanga mbu omwandu kukwe kulimutonyia tsinyanga tsioosi!"
  104,4,"Shikali kario tawe! Toto alikhuyungwa mu Hutwama."
  104,5,"Ne nishina shilakhwechesia mbu Hutwama nishina?"
  104,6,"Ni omulilo kwa Nyasaye okwawafibwa."
  104,7,"Okuninanga khumioyo."
  104,8,"Toto oko baliikalilwamwo."
  104,9,"Khutsisiilo tsiarambiyibwa po."
  105,1,"Koo, shiwalolakhwo shinga Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhola Abandu beyinzofu balia?"
  105,2,"Shiyakhola ebifwanga biabu biabiiya?"
  105,3,"Mana nabarumila amayoni emikanda nemikanda."
  105,4,"Mana nikabalasila amachina keliloba liomumulilo."
  105,5,"Mana nabakhola shinga obunyasi bunyanyilwe!"